&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a new challenge?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and passionate Mental Health Nurses to join our Bank Team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Joining our Bank is a great way to gain clinical skills while working in a flexible way to suit your lifestyle.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for flexible Mental Health nursing support in our forensic low secure inpatient service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are interested in developing your skills within this area of practice, this would be a fantastic opportunity. The team works within a strong recovery focus ethos, has a can do attitude and enjoys building therapeutic relationships with patients and being part of the MDT.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for effective and dedicated nurses to provide clinical care across two wards, supported by senior nurses and a comprehensive Multidisciplinary team.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will be responsible for delivering compassionate, evidence-based effective, high quality care under the named nurse CPA process in line with our model of care.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will be fully supported by the Team leader and Nursing Leads.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
